Motor A (Left motor):

enA (Speed control) → Pin 3 (PWM)

in1 (Direction) → Pin 8

in2 (Direction) → Pin 9

Motor A wire → OUT1

Motor A wire → OUT2

Motor B (Right motor):

enB (Speed control) → Pin 5 (PWM)

in3 (Direction) → Pin 10

in4 (Direction) → Pin 11

Motor B wire → OUT3

Motor B wire → OUT4

Left IR sensor output → Pin 2

Right IR sensor output → Pin 4

Ultrasonic Sensors (e.g., HC-SR04):
Front-Left Sensor:

Trig → Pin 6

Echo → Pin 7

Front-Right Sensor:

Trig → Pin 12

Echo → Pin 13

S0 → Analog Pin A0

S1 → Analog Pin A1

S2 → Analog Pin A2

S3 → Analog Pin A3

OUT → Analog Pin A4
